@AbapCatalog.viewEnhancementCategory: [#NONE]
@AccessControl.authorizationCheck: #NOT_REQUIRED
@EndUserText.label: 'DBS Log Datas覺'
@Metadata.ignorePropagatedAnnotations: true
define view entity YDBS_DDL_I_ALL_LOG
  as select from ydbs_t_log
{
  key companycode             as Companycode,
  key accountingdocument      as Accountingdocument,
  key fiscalyear              as Fiscalyear,
  key accountingdocumentitem  as Accountingdocumentitem,
      invoicenumber           as Invoicenumber,
      invoiceduedate          as Invoiceduedate,
      @Semantics.amount.currencyCode: 'Transactioncurrency'
      invoiceamount           as Invoiceamount,
      transactioncurrency     as Transactioncurrency,
      invoicestatus           as Invoicestatus,
      bankinternalid          as Bankinternalid,
      collect_document        as CollectDocument,
      collect_document_year   as CollectDocumentYear,
      clearing_document       as ClearingDocument,
      clearing_document_year  as ClearingDocumentYear,
      temporary_document      as TemporaryDocument,
      temporary_document_year as TemporaryDocumentYear,
      batch_id                as BatchId,
      trf_id                  as TrfId,
      invoice_id              as InvoiceId
}
